Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵就如同剑  如何使用取决于握剑之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只需让自己成为强大的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的使用者为达目的不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕剑刃沾满鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使剑被斩成两段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对此感到些许不安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:21.70,NOTE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Connected Passed Pawn\N————\N国际象棋术语「通路联兵」。\N升变(Promotion)指当兵到达底线时能升级为同色的象、马、车或后。\N而通路兵(Passed pawn)则是敌方无法阻止其前进的兵、因此很容易升变。\N通路联兵则指相邻的通路兵、因为可以共同前进、所以异常强大。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}誕生日だぜハッピー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是快乐的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺你  法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要下船？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们按照契约已经偷来15艘联邦战舰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽这么说  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会转告卡尔特法尔的大伙法姆留在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽不在的话  我一个人可飞不起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是还有米莉娅殿下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她掌握的知识足够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判断力也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人不适合做法姆导航员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要像米莉娅殿下那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽可是很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人一点都不厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆你是不会明白的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一印象可是糟糕透顶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和格拉吉艾斯的接触可是意料之外的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅侵犯了领空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在其领土内进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和野蛮人无异啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争无法避免了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧  即使交出希尔维乌斯也无济于事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了肯定会吓一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无敌的死神希尔维乌斯竟变得如此狼狈不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是先锋艇的队长阁下缺阵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损失或许就不会如此惨重了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是早点回来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不见法姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没脸见她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也不是米莉娅殿下的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换作姐姐大人就不会犹豫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤要凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检测数据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部参数正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊格纳斯大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂迪奥  这可不是在玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道该往哪飞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道  你绝对不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆你也说说他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:31.88,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返航
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  只要离开国境一点就不干涉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可难说  搞不好等会就带着同伴回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可得快点回收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微修理一下应该就能飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利地把它击坠了呢  法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要身在希尔维乌斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争就不可避免
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想下船就下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正她们原本也不是乘员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾里奥  联络
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,循环阀门修理完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  开始运转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始运转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输出功率上升
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40%  上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回卡尔特法尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本就是希尔维乌斯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩耍的时间已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你们一起飞的日子我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:09:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  吉泽说她想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1500出发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好要补给  顺便载你一段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉赛尔  我之前和你说的话还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也需要有话直说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在吉泽面前一直很任性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在我身边变得那么理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却一点也不了解她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身边也曾有这么一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对我很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所当然地要陪伴在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深信对方也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事实是怎样谁又知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经无法确认我的心意是否传达到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅殿下  着火了着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…土豆包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  土豆包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为法姆喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了好吃的东西就会打起精神不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做给你们吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这原本是图兰…国与国之间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明和你们没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们卷进来  给你们带来困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您根本不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆…法姆只是没法扔下米莉娅殿下不管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人一定要活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来成为你的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经不需要再呆在希尔维乌斯里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能回卡尔特法尔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人不适合做法姆导航员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要像米莉娅殿下那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆是不会对遇到麻烦的米莉娅殿下置之不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉赛尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我光想着自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对法姆说了过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明最不想看到她露出那种难过的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想帮法姆打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最不想看到法姆失落的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们尽是想着法姆的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么办法能让法姆打起精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是法姆的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉赛尔  今天还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是强人所难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想  首先啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们下船了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以说的委婉点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要挑卖相好  蒂也没有枯萎的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要1加仑牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你这所有的橙子和土豆全要了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽  要出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我  法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别偷懒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到个厉害的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是桅杆顶  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆  传球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下能突破防线了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先扳平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  听说在比赛曲棍球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这比赛真精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆那家伙真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰…舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  上啊  法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆·芳·方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有个更响亮的名字就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗里兹他们说叫起来像宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢  法姆·芳·方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会掉下来的啊  臭鸭子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿塔莫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像姐妹一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在那片天空下翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想化作一阵风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆  我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅公主殿下要不要也来玩玩看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆  又多了一名队员哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那谁来加入我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以为自己失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要帮助她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为孤身一人是很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要做她坚实的后盾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要做她们两人的后盾  直到永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想过我这关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅  接住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的人给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我该怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和吉泽一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了米莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:19:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和法姆一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天要让飞行大赛重新开赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}誕生日だぜHappy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}生まれて生きて　土に帰る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}おめでとう　おめでとう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}Happy Birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}Dear Fam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是快乐的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生至今  终将回归尘土
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你  祝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  趁热吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为法姆的眼泪干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:20:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  要对你保密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家偷偷地做了准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  15艘战舰的目标达成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要下船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕鲸还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起我就16岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒联邦  夺回图兰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我送你的生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来你们也成了希尔维乌斯的一员了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了欢迎我的到来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.87,0:22:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了  塔琪安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是安那托勒度西斯联合王国先遣军总司令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森特·阿尔锡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图兰流亡政权国王代理  米莉娅公主殿下
